- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the overall structure of the automated vehicle system, which falls under the domain of systems and control. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper discusses the software architecture of the automated vehicle system, which falls under the domain of software engineering. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction): The paper mentions the interaction with human operators, which falls under the domain of human-computer interaction.
